msgstr "Ajouter le texte ``0``."

msgid ""
"Set the \"Horizontal Alignment\" and \"Vertical Alignment\" to ``Center``."
msgstr ""
"Réglez \"Alignement horizontal\" et \"Alignement vertical\" sur \"Centre\"."

